00:48:21,519 --> 00:48:23,395
He fell off the jungle gym.

590
00:48:24,313 --> 00:48:25,523
He had a plane in his hand.

591
00:48:25,773 --> 00:48:27,024
I'm just about through.

592
00:48:27,274 --> 00:48:29,235
- Don't hurt him.
- I won't hurt him.

593
00:48:29,443 --> 00:48:32,196
Mr. Kramer, can I talk to you outside?

594
00:48:32,446 --> 00:48:33,822
Yeah. Can she come in?

595
00:48:34,114 --> 00:48:35,032
Margaret, come in.

596
00:48:35,741 --> 00:48:37,535
- Stay, Daddy.
- I'll be right back.

597
00:48:37,785 --> 00:48:40,621
- Daddy, stay.
