598
00:48:40,955 --> 00:48:42,206
It's all right, darling.

599
00:48:42,540 --> 00:48:43,999
I'm just talking to the doctor.

600
00:48:45,167 --> 00:48:46,335
He'll be right back.

601
00:48:46,585 --> 00:48:47,503
I'm right here.

