615
00:50:29,188 --> 00:50:29,980
How is he?

616
00:50:30,356 --> 00:50:33,442
He's okay. He's sleeping.

617
00:50:33,943 --> 00:50:36,153
It's okay. I can do that.

618
00:50:38,239 --> 00:50:40,991
Ted, I'm so sorry.
I feel responsible.

619
00:50:41,408 --> 00:50:42,868
I don't know what happened.

620
00:50:43,452 --> 00:50:46,997
One minute he was there and the
next he was lying on the ground.

621
00:50:48,249 --> 00:50:49,708
Come on, Margaret.

622
00:50:50,417 --> 00:50:53,254
Now listen, I want
to ask you a favour, okay?

