00:51:00,469 --> 00:51:02,972
...but if a building fell on me...

626
00:51:03,430 --> 00:51:07,393
...would you consider
taking care of Billy?

627
00:51:11,689 --> 00:51:15,192
I want you to know that I put
some thought into this...

628
00:51:15,442 --> 00:51:16,277
...and I...

629
00:51:17,236 --> 00:51:20,155
...can't think of anybody else
I would trust with him.

630
00:51:20,823 --> 00:51:23,492
I know you'd be okay
with him because...

631
00:51:25,286 --> 00:51:26,996
...you're a good mother.

