playground. He cut himself.

650
00:53:07,333 --> 00:53:10,169
It was scary.
I ran him to the hospital.

651
00:53:10,378 --> 00:53:12,672
He has a little scar,
but he'll be fine.

652
00:53:12,922 --> 00:53:15,258
I've been worrying
that it's my fault...

653
00:53:15,550 --> 00:53:18,803
Don't do that. You can't even
see it from a distance.

654
00:53:22,348 --> 00:53:26,561
I sit in the coffee shop across
from his school and watch him.

655
00:53:26,811 --> 00:53:28,187
He got so big.

656
00:53:28,396 --> 00:53:29,855
You've been watching him?

