00:53:30,106 --> 00:53:32,233
I've been in New York for
about two months now.

658
00:53:32,483 --> 00:53:33,693
I didn't know that.

659
00:53:34,527 --> 00:53:35,987
Anyway...

660
00:53:36,529 --> 00:53:39,282
That's why I wanted
to talk to you today.

661
00:53:40,157 --> 00:53:44,954
Last time you saw me,
I was in pretty bad...

662
00:53:45,329 --> 00:53:46,956
- Shaky?
- Really bad shape.

663
00:53:47,206 --> 00:53:48,749
Yeah, I was.

664
00:53:49,208 --> 00:53:50,126
I was.

665
00:53:51,168 --> 00:53:53,296
Well, you look lovely now.

