If I play rough...

707
00:56:19,066 --> 00:56:22,320
...you can bet they will too.
Can you take that?

708
00:56:22,528 --> 00:56:23,529
Yes.

709
00:56:24,447 --> 00:56:26,574
And it's going to cost you $15,000.

710
00:56:28,492 --> 00:56:29,535
That's if we win.

711
00:56:29,911 --> 00:56:32,496
If we go to appeal,
it'll cost you more.

712
00:56:33,789 --> 00:56:34,790
I understand.

713
00:56:36,751 --> 00:56:38,794
Now, how old is the child again?

714
00:56:39,086 --> 00:56:40,630
My son is 7.

715
00:56:40,922 --> 00:56:42,548
- That's tough.
- Why?

716
00:56:42,840 --> 00:56:46,969
In cases involving a child that young,
the court tends to side with her.

717
00:56:47,261 --> 00:56:48,471
She signed over custody.

718
00:56:48,763 --> 00:56:52,308
I'm not saying we don't have a shot,
but it won't be easy.

719
00:56:52,642 --> 00:56:54,435
Do me a favour, will you?

720
00:56:54,727 --> 00:56:57,563
